    nn0z syl 3eqtr3d w3a c2 cexp gcdcl syl2an 3adant2 3syl simp13 mulcom simpl3
    sqval wa eqeq1d biimp3a oveq12d simp11 simp12 oveq2d mulgcdr ancoms 3adant1
    sylan cabs 3ad2ant3 gcdid oveq1d simp2 gcdabs1 eqtrd gcdass 3eqtr4d biimpar
    cfv gcdcom 3adant3 mulid1 3eqtrrd 3expia ) ADEZBFEZCDEZUAZABGHCGHZIJZCUBUCH
